From: Saarthi Dev <fix@saarthi.ai>
Date: Sun, 21 Jun 2026 05:25:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add rich background design + dummy login credentials

Changes:
- Login.jsx: Beautiful redesigned page with glassmorphism card, decorative
  mandala SVGs, gradient blobs, demo credentials panel with one-click
  auto-fill buttons (Student/Amma/Senior/Business), show/hide password toggle
- auth.js: Added 5 demo users (demo@saarthi.ai / student / amma / senior /
  business) that work instantly without any backend - offline-first auth
- AuthContext.jsx: Skip backend getProfile() call for demo tokens so no
  network errors on demo login
- globals.css: Enhanced Indian art backgrounds from 3% to 8-9% opacity for
  visible paisley/lotus/jali patterns; added warm ivory gradient body
  background; paisley overlay on entire #root; dashboard mobile responsive CSS

Demo credentials:
  demo@saarthi.ai     / Demo@1234
  student@saarthi.ai  / Student@123
  amma@saarthi.ai     / Amma@123
  senior@saarthi.ai   / Senior@123
  business@saarthi.ai / Biz@12345
